Dataset Name: Rupture and Deliver TGT Barcode Counting
Dataset Design: U251 cells were incubated on RAD-TGT coated surfaces, cells were removed and lysed. Barcodes from RAD-TGTs (synthetic oligos) were PCR amplified and subsequent amplicons had illumina tails added via PCR
Dataset Assay: CRISPR, Flow Cytometry, Next Generation Sequencing, Fluorescence Microscopy
